{"tid":2006652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懲教署：禤雅達（職員編號：AO1700）呢幾日係按編更休假 無停職 放假後會復工","createTime":"2020-05-08T02:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T05:24:54.000Z","uid":22556,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6a13fd80191c093be0aeaaf4b007bcc8e2519e77","tid":2006652,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:39:35.000Z","msg":"日前有曾在壁屋懲教所還柙的示威者投訴被懲教職員虐打，包括被「落雞翼」、撼頭埋牆等，其中一級懲教助理禤雅達（職員編號：AO1700）被點名指有份掌摑唱《願榮光歸香港》的抗爭者，及以知道其家人地址，威脅他們不能公開事件（詳見報道）。香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒今午在 Facebook 表示，從可靠消息得知禤雅達目前已經休假。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署回覆《立場新聞》查詢時表示，禤雅達現時按既定編更安排放取假期，假期後會返回壁屋懲教所工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A3%81%E5%B1%8B%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%B6%89%E8%99%90%E6%89%93%E9%82%84%E6%9F%99%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92-%E6%B6%89%E4%BA%8B%E8%80%85%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E4%BC%91%E5%81%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A3%2581%25E5%25B1%258B%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259F%2599%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%2581%2587%2F&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=099c036f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A3%2581%25E5%25B1%258B%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259F%2599%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%2581%2587%2F&h=59771d42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A3%81%E5%B1%8B%E6%